# Build a image
$ docker build .

# Tagging one image
$ docker build -t marodrigues20/redis:latest .

Note: marodrigues20 -> my docker id
      redis  -> Repo/Project Name
      latest -> Version
      .      -> Specify the directory of files/folders to use for the build


  

# How to create one image from one container that is running
$ docker commit -c 'CMD ["linux command"]' <container id>

